egral scales characteristic of a real supernova, the\nflame structure is predicted to become complex and unsteady. Implications for a\npossible transition to detonation are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Nov 2008 22:23:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
