 suggested. A large\nsymmetry repulsion at high baryon density will also lead to an \"earlier\"\nhadron-deconfinement transition in n-rich matter. A suitable treatment of the\nisovector interaction in the partonic EoS appears very relevant.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Nov 2008 10:44:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
